/**

 * Copy this file to mail.local.php and fill in your SMTP credentials.

 * mail.local.php is loaded by config/mail.php and should NOT be committed to git.

 *

 * Or use Admin → Settings → Email Configuration (writes mail.local.php automatically).
 *
 * Environment variables (override constants when set):
 *   SMTP_HOST, SMTP_PORT, SMTP_USERNAME, SMTP_PASSWORD, SMTP_ENCRYPTION
 *   SMTP_FROM_EMAIL, SMTP_FROM_NAME, SMTP_REPLY_TO, SMTP_USE (true/false)

 *

 * Gmail: App Password — https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords

 * SendGrid: username "apikey", password = your API key

 * Brevo: username = your Brevo login email, password = SMTP key from Brevo dashboard

 */



